# Prior Knowledge
guide:PriorKnowledge_CS rdf:type guide:RequiredKnowledge ;
    guide:previousKnowledge "An undergraduate level course on computer security is desired but not required. Some demonstrable knowledge on the basic principles of computer security is necessary." .